title: East Side - 1 Bedroom Apartment
posting_body: This complex is within walking distance to downtown and other activities on the East side of Austin.
Notable hotspots nearby include Old Thousand and Franklin's BBQ.
Units have unique layouts and finishes, which include washer and dryer in each unit.
Resort style amenities are found throughout the property, which include a swimming pool and fitness center.
This is a pet friendly property!
